1
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,079
"Pure and innocent"!

2
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,680
Sister, what does that mean?

3
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,519
Nothing.

4
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,920
[Why did he put up]

5
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,200
[the paperweight I gave him as a prize?]

6
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,439
[Not good.]

7
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,879
[He thinks the prize I offered]

8
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,680
[was far too valuable.]

9
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,120
[He's hinting at me.]

10
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:49,760
[True.]

11
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:51,359
[There are too many people here today.]

12
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:53,079
[So many eyes are watching.]

13
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,400
[No.]

14
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,840
[No matter what,]

15
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,959
[I must win that paperweight back.]

16
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,400
[Then no one will think]

17
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,120
[I was deliberately giving the Chen family a gift.]

18
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,799
[If I clear my name,]

19
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,799
[his name will be cleared too.]

20
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,519
This is a fine piece.

21
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,000
This jade paperweight

22
00:02:07,239 --> 00:02:08,560
looks very valuable.

23
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,800
The Chen family truly is wealthy.

24
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:12,800
Wealthy?

25
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,800
Squeezed from the people.

26
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,120
Two realms split by one beam.

27
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,639
The greater bows to the small.

28
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,879
Five warriors above,

29
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:26,319
can't beat a pair below.

30
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,240
Guess the object.

31
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,800
What large and small kingdoms?

32
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,800
This object of yours

33
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,280
must be a spirit-writing stick

34
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,159
and a Daoist sand tray.

35
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,159
Wrong.
How is that wrong?

36
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,159
Didn't you ask me

37
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:39,199
to find a Daoist for you?

38
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,439
Anyway, your answer is wrong.

39
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:44,680
Stop being so cryptic.

40
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,199
Only green willows may tether a horse.

41
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,039
Only

42
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,199
green... horse...

43
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:02,199
Sunlight over a gushing spring.

44
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,680
Brother Ye,

45
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,800
the place in your riddle

46
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,680
isn't somewhere you've been, is it?

47
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,319
Of course it is.

48
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:12,479
But Brother Ye,

49
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:14,199
you've traveled far and wide.

50
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,520
The places you've been

51
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,759
are places others have never seen.

52
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,240
Isn't it unfair

53
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,680
to set such a riddle?

54
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:21,960
Then I'll withdraw the riddle

55
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:23,039
and stop playing.
No, don't.

56
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,560
What if someone guesses it?

57
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,840
I know the answer.

58
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,280
Sunlight over a gushing spring.

59
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,039
Is it Yangquan?

60
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,639
Correct.

61
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,039
Here.

62
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,319
I'll have someone
send you gunpowder.

63
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,039
Thank you, Lord Ye.

64
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,240
How did you guess it?

65
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:46,840
My ancestral home is in Shanxi.

66
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,599
This guessing game isn't fun at all.

67
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,680
Such a dawdler.

68
00:03:57,879 --> 00:04:00,080
Green willow means the wood radical.

69
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,039
Tethering a horse

70
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,919
must be the other half.

71
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,159
Is it qiang, meaning mast?

72
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,680
Wrong.

73
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,360
Aunt, try again.

74
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,000
It's chu, meaning pestle.

75
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:16,000
Green willow means the wood radical.

76
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,040
Can tether a horse—

77
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,639
Among the earthly branches,

78
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:19,839
Horse corresponds to wu.

79
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,160
So the character is chu.

80
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,279
Miss Gu is correct.

81
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:27,040
How impressive.

82
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,360
Miss Gu is amazing.

83
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:45,199
Large kingdom, small kingdom...

84
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,160
I know the answer.

85
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,360
Wrong guess.

86
00:04:58,399 --> 00:04:59,759
Still haven't guessed it.

87
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,959
Isn't that Young Master Wang?

88
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,360
Let's go take a look.

89
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:18,120
Cousin.

90
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,319
What are you doing here?

91
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,920
I just came out of the privy

92
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,839
and lost my way.

93
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:24,519
I wandered into a room

94
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,480
and happened to see this painting on the desk.

95
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,439
It suits my taste perfectly.

96
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:28,879
May I ask who painted it?

97
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,959
Could I have it?

98
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,800
This painting has lofty spirit.

99
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,800
It looks like Xuruo's work.

100
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,720
I don't think so.

101
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,800
Why?

102
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:40,560
Look at the inscription.

103
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,439
"How small the other peaks appear!"

104
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,680
It's Taige style, a formal court script.

105
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:47,040
Precise, powerful, and dignified.

106
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,240
Without more than ten years of practice,

107
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:50,839
one couldn't write characters like this.

108
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,040
But Young Master Chen

109
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,800
is so young.

110
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,399
How could he have written it?

111
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:59,160
Miss Gu is right.

112
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,120
It was indeed not painted by me.

113
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:05,279
Then what do you think of it?

114
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,560
I think

115
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,560
this painting is not only grand,

116
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,120
but also carries

117
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,040
the force of reaching the summit

118
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,279
and seeing all other peaks below.

119
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,319
It's just...

120
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,680
Only what?

121
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,199
It feels somewhat hollow,

122
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,199
not like true feeling.

123
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,279
Well said.

124
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,240
Brother.

125
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,800
Greetings, Mr. Chen.
Uncle.

126
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,800
Lord Ye.

127
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,600
Young Master Wang.

128
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:45,000
Then tell me,

129
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,399
who painted

130
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:49,000
this Ascending the Heights?

131
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:54,360
It should be an older

132
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,759
and highly respected teacher.

133
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,319
Older?

134
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,519
Highly respected?

135
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,000
Uncle.

136
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,720
Miss Gu did not mean it.

137
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,519
This painting

138
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,199
was done by you?

139
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:11,199
My apologies.

140
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,920
I spoke out of turn.

141
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:13,959
I dared to

142
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,399
judge your fine work so rashly.

143
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,720
Please forgive me.

144
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,800
I say,

145
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,879
since you are here as a guest,

146
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,439
why be so afraid?

147
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:24,360
It's all right.

148
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,120
Once a painting is completed,

149
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,000
it is meant to be judged.

150
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,360
Miss Gu need not apologize.

151
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,439
Exactly.

152
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,000
They say a minister's heart can hold a boat.

153
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:36,839
Lord Chen is not yet a prime minister,

154
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,360
but he's nearly in the Secretariat.

155
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,959
So, half a boat at least.

156
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,560
But for a dignified prime minister

157
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,160
to hide behind a door and eavesdrop—

158
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:45,560
that lacks grace.

159
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:48,560
Someone wanted to critique my painting.

160
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,000
It is only natural

161
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:51,720
that I wished to hear it.

162
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,319
So it was Lord Chen's painting.

163
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,079
Then may I have it?

164
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,600
Since Young Master Wang likes it,

165
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,000
take it.

166
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,600
Thank you, Lord Chen.

167
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:05,759
Actually, I came to find Lord Ye.

168
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:08,160
Lord Ye is of noble character,

169
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:11,000
and serves as the Crown Prince's reader.

170
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,600
It is getting late.

171
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:14,160
I fear

172
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,040
he should return.

173
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,199
I still have a riddle unsolved.

174
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:21,240
I'm not going back.

175
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,319
What kind of riddle

176
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,720
could stump Lord Ye?

177
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:31,879
Uncle.

178
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:34,240
It is a riddle from Miss Gu.

179
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,960
It has stumped everyone.

180
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,799
Let's hear it, then.

181
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,360
Two realms split by one beam.

182
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:42,120
The greater bows to the small.

183
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:44,080
Five warriors above,

184
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,960
can't beat a pair below.

185
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,039
Guess the object.

186
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,759
Isn't that an abacus?

187
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,279
You actually guessed it.

188
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,039
I'll have the prize sent

189
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:55,080
to you at once.

190
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:56,799
You call that hard?

191
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,320
What?

192
00:08:59,240 --> 00:08:59,960
With so many of you here,
no one guessed it?

193
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,320
You all...

194
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,360
Uncle.

195
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:51,879
Earlier I went to visit Fourth Uncle.

196
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,360
He refused to see me.

197
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,240
Later, Grandmother came as well.

198
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,440
Fourth Uncle still would not see her.

199
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:57,960
Only after Grandmother said

200
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,080
she would summon a physician

201
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,399
did he open the gate.

202
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,559
Let's not speak of him.

203
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:05,759
For next spring's imperial exam,

204
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:07,200
do you plan to sit for it?

205
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:09,360
That is my intention.

206
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,120
I plan to return to the academy tomorrow

207
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,639
and shut myself in to study.

208
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:14,159
Good.

209
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,840
Tomorrow, take your essays

210
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:20,360
to Minister Chang Tinglan's residence

211
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,320
and ask him for guidance.

212
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,679
I have already spoken with him.

213
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:23,759
From now on,

214
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,039
every ten days,

215
00:10:25,559 --> 00:10:27,120
he will review an essay for you.

216
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,919
Lord Chang?

217
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,519
But he is not a great scholar.

218
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:40,000
Yes, Third Uncle.

219
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:41,000
Go.

220
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:57,000
I think

221
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:59,279
this painting is not only grand,

222
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,039
but also carries

223
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:02,960
the force of reaching the summit

224
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:05,840
and seeing all other peaks below.

225
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:10,080
It's just...

226
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:12,840
It feels somewhat hollow,

227
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,919
not like true feeling.

228
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,159
True feeling.

229
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,759
Miss,

230
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:20,440
incense burns so strongly at Baoxiang Temple.

231
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:22,600
Yes. Today is the Double Ninth Festival.

232
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:24,080
Not everyone is here to pray.

233
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:26,039
Some may be here to climb heights.

234
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,720
Let's hurry forward.

235
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,879
After praying for Grandmother,

236
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:31,000
we can come back and look around.

237
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:31,960
Yes, miss.

238
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,600
Look.

239
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,559
Autumn shadows fill the river; wild geese take wing.

240
00:12:58,639 --> 00:13:01,519
With wine and friends, I climb the emerald height.

241
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:04,159
What a pity.

242
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,679
I didn't bring good wine.

243
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,440
A rare day off

244
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:09,159
should be spent resting properly.

245
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,000
Why insist on climbing a mountain?

246
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,600
Uncle, you can't run.

247
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:20,080
I secretly brought you here to climb.

248
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,200
If anything happens to you,

249
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,679
my mother will skin me alive.

250
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:26,639
Uncle.
Uncle.

251
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,480
Uncle.
My lord.

252
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,200
Uncle, don't scare me.

253
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:31,600
Uncle.
My lord.

254
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,000
Bodhisattva above,

255
00:13:35,519 --> 00:13:36,600
please protect Grandmother.

256
00:13:37,159 --> 00:13:38,080
May she be safe

257
00:13:38,559 --> 00:13:39,399
and free from disaster.

258
00:13:58,159 --> 00:13:58,679
Miss.

259
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:01,480
Isn't that Lord Ye?

260
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:02,759
Go see.

261
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,200
Cousin Jinzhao.

262
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:06,600
What happened to Lord Ye?

263
00:14:06,879 --> 00:14:08,039
His heart may be acting up.

264
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,200
If you know it is his heart ailment,

265
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,399
do you have medicine with you?

266
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,960
He usually keeps medicine on him.

267
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,600
But he happened to be off duty today,

268
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:16,600
so he didn't bring any.

269
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,039
Guard Li went down
to call a physician.

270
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,320
I understand.

271
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:22,200
A heart ailment cannot wait.

272
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,399
No.

273
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,440
We can't wait for Guard Li.

274
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:32,799
Qingpu.

275
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,480
Press his Tanzhong pressure point.

276
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,360
Yes.

277
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:36,519
Please move aside.

278
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,399
Will this work?

279
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,759
What are you doing?

280
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,000
If you harm him,

281
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,080
our whole family could die.

282
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,399
But we can't just watch him die.

283
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,200
Let go. But...

284
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,559
No buts.

285
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,519
He moved.

286
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:12,759
Miss, it's working.

287
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:13,960
It really is.

288
00:15:28,159 --> 00:15:28,960
It's you.

289
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,120
You're awake.

290
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,360
Thank heaven.

291
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:34,360
Don't move.
Bodhisattva bless us.

292
00:15:35,559 --> 00:15:36,320
Do you still

293
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:37,559
feel unwell anywhere?

294
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,519
Yes.
Where?

295
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,039
My hand.

296
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:45,080
My hand is trapped.

297
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:11,679
On the road, go slower if you must,

298
00:16:11,799 --> 00:16:12,679
but don't jostle him.

299
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:13,720
Yes.

300
00:16:15,039 --> 00:16:15,799
And you too.

301
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:16,919
Don't move around.

302
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,320
Even after taking medicine,

303
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:20,000
you should rest for several days.

304
00:16:21,519 --> 00:16:23,480
Why such a nag at your age?

305
00:16:23,799 --> 00:16:24,600
What did you say?

306
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,120
I said,

307
00:16:27,559 --> 00:16:29,440
you're so young, yet such a nag,

308
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,440
like an old nanny.

309
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,120
Lift the sedan.

310
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,480
Let's go too.

311
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,919
The Marquis of Changxing leads the military lords.

312
00:16:58,399 --> 00:17:00,759
Ye Xian is his heir.

313
00:17:01,399 --> 00:17:03,240
With a heart ailment, he cannot take up arms.

314
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,440
And he is the marquisate's only son.

315
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:08,119
If the military heir cannot fight,

316
00:17:08,279 --> 00:17:09,440
he has no future.

317
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:11,279
Yes.

318
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:13,519
A heart ailment is hard to cure.

319
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,519
Miss,

320
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:24,599
you are amazing.

321
00:17:30,039 --> 00:17:30,960
It is getting late.

322
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,039
We've been out for half a day.

323
00:17:32,279 --> 00:17:33,119
We should go back.

324
00:17:33,839 --> 00:17:34,319
Let's go.

325
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,759
When can we pass?

326
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,079
I still have things to do.

327
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,319
I need to go home.

328
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:51,519
Miss, I'll ask.

329
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,920
When will they let us through?

330
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,200
Can't someone give us an answer?

331
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,440
Say something.

332
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,240
When can we pass?

333
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,599
Miss, I heard

334
00:18:09,599 --> 00:18:11,279
a noble has come to Baoxiang Temple to offer incense.

335
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:12,759
The whole mountain is sealed off.

336
00:18:13,599 --> 00:18:14,400
Offer incense?

337
00:18:14,799 --> 00:18:15,960
That's clearly a lie.

338
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:17,960
People offer incense early, not late.

339
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,119
It is already afternoon.

340
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:20,559
Who comes to offer incense now?

341
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,599
What rotten luck.

342
00:18:23,279 --> 00:18:23,839
Had I known,

343
00:18:23,839 --> 00:18:25,200
I would have gone down with Ye Xian.

344
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:29,519
When I climbed the tree earlier,

345
00:18:29,559 --> 00:18:30,839
I saw on that hill

346
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:31,759
another path.

347
00:18:32,079 --> 00:18:33,279
Why don't I go scout it first?

348
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:34,200
If it can be used,
I'll come back for you.

349
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:35,960
All right.
Then wait for me.

350
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:50,960
Let us through.

351
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,519
We need to go down.

352
00:18:52,799 --> 00:18:53,680
Exactly.

353
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:55,119
We need to go down.

354
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:02,920
Why isn't Qingpu back yet?

355
00:19:04,759 --> 00:19:06,000
Could something have happened?

356
00:19:18,319 --> 00:19:19,960
Is this the path Qingpu mentioned?

357
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,480
Why is there no one here?

358
00:19:34,799 --> 00:19:35,920
Why isn't there a soul here?

359
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:57,920
Help!

360
00:19:59,359 --> 00:20:00,359
Mr. Chen!

361
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,079
Protect the Crown Prince.

362
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:19,079
Yes.

363
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,599
So the man that day

364
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,000
really was him.

365
00:21:45,599 --> 00:21:46,279
Damned Crown Prince.

366
00:21:46,359 --> 00:21:47,559
Die!

367
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,640
Can you still stand?

368
00:22:56,079 --> 00:22:56,759
Were you frightened?

369
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,160
What?

370
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,240
You mean

371
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,759
Jinzhao is still on the mountain?

372
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:10,799
Yes.

373
00:23:11,359 --> 00:23:12,680
I found a path in the back hills

374
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:14,039
and planned to return for Miss.

375
00:23:14,319 --> 00:23:15,920
But who would have thought the way back

376
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:16,960
was also sealed off?

377
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,359
So I came back first
and inform you all.

378
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:21,240
It will soon be dark.

379
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,720
Please give me more people, Madam,

380
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,119
to go back up the mountain and find Miss.

381
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:25,119
Good child.

382
00:23:25,559 --> 00:23:26,759
You may have as many as you need.

383
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,240
Take my tally at once

384
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,079
and summon people.
Come, Nanny Zhao.

385
00:23:32,759 --> 00:23:33,480
Thank you, Madam.

386
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:34,680
Go.

387
00:23:38,119 --> 00:23:38,960
In my view,

388
00:23:39,279 --> 00:23:39,920
Jinzhao

389
00:23:40,319 --> 00:23:41,480
is just too playful.

390
00:23:44,039 --> 00:23:45,279
Jinzhao is not that kind of person.

391
00:23:47,759 --> 00:23:48,640
What are we to do?

392
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:55,920
Will you confess or not?

393
00:23:58,759 --> 00:23:59,759
Still refusing?

394
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:12,680
I've already seen him

395
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,839
kill people twice.

396
00:24:14,319 --> 00:24:15,759
Will he kill me to silence me?

397
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:28,200
Greetings, Mr. Chen.

398
00:24:33,599 --> 00:24:34,240
Mr. Chen.

399
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:35,720
I truly heard nothing.

400
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:36,880
I saw nothing.

401
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:37,440
I promise.

402
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,599
I won't say a single word.

403
00:24:39,039 --> 00:24:39,640
Please.

404
00:24:40,039 --> 00:24:41,759
Please spare my life.

405
00:24:47,119 --> 00:24:48,519
Today's matter is gravely serious.

406
00:24:48,799 --> 00:24:49,759
If word gets out,

407
00:24:50,039 --> 00:24:51,279
who knows how many people

408
00:24:51,519 --> 00:24:53,039
it could bring death upon them.

409
00:25:02,799 --> 00:25:03,839
This is...

410
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:07,720
Take it.

411
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,960
I cannot protect you otherwise.

412
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,160
It's poison.

413
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:14,640
Mr. Chen.

414
00:25:15,039 --> 00:25:15,759
I won't breathe

415
00:25:15,759 --> 00:25:16,799
a single word of it.

416
00:25:17,200 --> 00:25:17,759
Otherwise,

417
00:25:18,119 --> 00:25:19,000
may lightning strike me.

418
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,440
No need for oaths.

419
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,720
Take the medicine.

420
00:25:25,279 --> 00:25:26,519
Then I will believe you.

421
00:25:27,079 --> 00:25:27,960
Mr. Chen.

422
00:25:28,559 --> 00:25:29,640
When I came today,

423
00:25:29,799 --> 00:25:31,240
many people saw me.

424
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:32,599
My maid and I

425
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:34,079
were together at first,

426
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:36,039
but then we got separated.

427
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:36,880
I imagine by now

428
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,079
she has already gone back.

429
00:25:38,359 --> 00:25:39,000
If she finds
she cannot find me,

430
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:41,599
she will surely send word when she returns.

431
00:25:42,119 --> 00:25:44,000
She may even report it to officials.

432
00:25:44,799 --> 00:25:45,400
Right.

433
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:46,799
On the way,

434
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,640
Lord Ye saw me too.

435
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,440
If he suddenly learns I died,

436
00:25:50,559 --> 00:25:51,960
he will certainly ask about it.

437
00:25:52,279 --> 00:25:53,279
So what?

438
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:54,720
If too many people ask,

439
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,160
then everyone will know.

440
00:25:57,599 --> 00:25:58,400
So killing me

441
00:25:58,599 --> 00:25:59,799
would do more harm than good.

442
00:26:00,279 --> 00:26:02,200
And this is sacred Buddhist ground.

443
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,319
Killing here is unlucky.

444
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,400
Please, Mr. Chen.

445
00:26:04,759 --> 00:26:06,279
Why not spare my life?

446
00:26:07,119 --> 00:26:08,599
Saving a life earns great merit.

447
00:26:08,839 --> 00:26:10,559
The dead are the only truly reliable ones.

448
00:26:11,559 --> 00:26:12,559
When today's matter is done,

449
00:26:13,079 --> 00:26:14,680
I will naturally protect your grandmother

450
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,759
and the Ji family

451
00:26:16,279 --> 00:26:17,480
and keep them safe.

452
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:45,960
Lord Chen.

453
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:48,200
Why must you do this?

454
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,400
Since you say the girl is one of us,

455
00:26:50,599 --> 00:26:51,799
she can naturally be trusted.

456
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:53,599
Trustworthy or not,

457
00:26:54,599 --> 00:26:56,640
I trust only what I test myself.

458
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,599
How did it go on your side?

459
00:27:01,519 --> 00:27:02,440
He confessed.

460
00:27:03,839 --> 00:27:04,759
Let's talk inside.

461
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:12,720
After all that questioning,

462
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,519
he only said the leader's surname is Xiao.

463
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,119
Every time they met,

464
00:27:16,119 --> 00:27:16,880
he wore a veiled hat,

465
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,000
his face was hidden.

466
00:27:19,799 --> 00:27:21,160
From his bearing,

467
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,079
he seemed like a scholar.

468
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:23,240
He spent freely.

469
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:26,680
When one of their men died before,

470
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:28,440
the compensation money

471
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,759
was a full five hundred taels.

472
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,240
That is why each of them

473
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:32,920
was willing to die for him.

474
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,720
Surname Xiao?

475
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,400
Could it be Xiao Qishan?

476
00:27:39,759 --> 00:27:40,880
Wasn't he once an adviser

477
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,000
to the late Prince Chengqing?

478
00:27:42,759 --> 00:27:44,079
Back then, Prince Chengqing

479
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:45,599
obeyed that man in everything.

480
00:27:46,079 --> 00:27:48,319
After Prince Chengqing's rebellion failed,

481
00:27:48,759 --> 00:27:50,200
The Marquis killed the prince,

482
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:52,400
and that adviser vanished.

483
00:27:52,839 --> 00:27:54,519
This time, the news of the Crown Prince leaving the palace

484
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:55,240
was leaked by us

485
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:56,759
to Prince Glorian.

486
00:27:58,119 --> 00:27:59,480
But Prince Glorian actually used

487
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,119
one of Prince Chengqing's former strategists.

488
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:02,680
That means...

489
00:28:02,839 --> 00:28:04,000
It means Prince Glorian

490
00:28:04,559 --> 00:28:05,920
has always brooded

491
00:28:06,319 --> 00:28:07,720
over Prince Chengqing's death.

492
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:13,079
It seems Prince Glorian

493
00:28:13,359 --> 00:28:14,759
is plotting something big.

494
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:16,599
Lord Chen,

495
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,519
you must be extra careful.

496
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,759
Same to you.

497
00:28:23,079 --> 00:28:23,799
Lord Chen.

498
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,680
We are in the same boat now.

499
00:28:27,839 --> 00:28:29,400
Back then, the late Prince Chengqing's rebellion

500
00:28:29,759 --> 00:28:31,960
left the Criminal Justice Office in ruins.

501
00:28:32,519 --> 00:28:33,559
If the Chief Councilor

502
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:35,400
had not valued us,

503
00:28:35,599 --> 00:28:36,359
how could we have

504
00:28:36,359 --> 00:28:37,640
to handle such an important case?

505
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:39,279
In the future,

506
00:28:39,839 --> 00:28:41,960
I hope you will support me, Lord Chen.

507
00:28:42,319 --> 00:28:43,920
You and I both serve our teacher.

508
00:28:44,359 --> 00:28:45,240
We should

509
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:47,000
work as one.

510
00:29:03,559 --> 00:29:04,279
Stop pretending.

511
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,160
Get up.

512
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,799
Greetings, Mr. Chen.

513
00:29:16,119 --> 00:29:17,079
Rise and speak.

514
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:23,799
It's over now.

515
00:29:27,680 --> 00:29:28,640
When today's matter is done,

516
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:30,799
I will naturally protect your grandmother

517
00:29:30,799 --> 00:29:31,920
and the Ji family

518
00:29:32,319 --> 00:29:33,599
and keep them safe.

519
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,799
Thank you for saving me just now, Mr. Chen.

520
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,319
What is it?
What are you looking at?

521
00:30:03,559 --> 00:30:04,799
I'm looking at you.

522
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:06,240
You seem

523
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,519
different from before.

524
00:30:09,119 --> 00:30:11,359
I mean that time I set fire to the storeroom

525
00:30:11,599 --> 00:30:13,279
and snatched your lantern.

526
00:30:14,599 --> 00:30:16,039
Why didn't you say so the last two times?

527
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:19,519
Because I didn't dare.

528
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,200
This time, I dare.

529
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,400
You just saved my life.

530
00:30:26,799 --> 00:30:28,119
You were too afraid to say it

531
00:30:28,119 --> 00:30:29,240
because you saw me kill?

532
00:30:30,359 --> 00:30:32,160
You only killed when you had no choice.

533
00:30:33,119 --> 00:30:34,200
How am I different?

534
00:30:37,279 --> 00:30:38,359
I can't quite say.

535
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,240
It reminds me

536
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:44,000
of when I lived in Tongzhou.

537
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,160
There was

538
00:30:45,519 --> 00:30:46,759
a young servant named Gou

539
00:30:46,759 --> 00:30:48,079
who played with me often.

540
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:50,000
We often played together.

541
00:30:50,799 --> 00:30:52,640
But one year he returned to his hometown.

542
00:30:52,799 --> 00:30:53,720
After he came back,

543
00:30:53,839 --> 00:30:55,200
his whole nature changed.

544
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,559
He became quiet

545
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,240
and stopped playing with me.

546
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,680
He only begged Grandmother

547
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,039
to send him to Suzhou

548
00:31:02,240 --> 00:31:03,440
as an apprentice in a shop.

549
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:06,480
I only learned later

550
00:31:07,599 --> 00:31:08,920
that during that month,

551
00:31:09,079 --> 00:31:10,279
his father had died.

552
00:31:12,119 --> 00:31:13,799
I shall watch from heaven

553
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:15,960
whether Great Yan

554
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,759
under your protection, Chen Yanyun,

555
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:21,160
can prosper without end.

556
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:40,079
I'm not saying you are like him.

557
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:41,319
What I mean is—

558
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,680
I understand.

559
00:31:48,119 --> 00:31:48,640
Sit.

560
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:56,079
My ancestral home is also in Tongzhou.

561
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,440
Even now,

562
00:31:57,839 --> 00:31:59,039
your grandmother still manages it.

563
00:32:04,279 --> 00:32:05,839
I wonder when

564
00:32:05,839 --> 00:32:07,319
I can return to Tongzhou.

565
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:09,440
What is it?

566
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,200
Do you dislike the capital?

567
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,000
I don't like the capital.

568
00:32:14,119 --> 00:32:15,319
The capital isn't fun at all.

569
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:16,680
Unlike Tongzhou,

570
00:32:18,799 --> 00:32:19,759
there are docks,

571
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:20,880
temple fairs,

572
00:32:21,319 --> 00:32:22,359
and book markets.

573
00:32:23,319 --> 00:32:25,119
The capital has those too.

574
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:26,799
The capital is different.

575
00:32:27,039 --> 00:32:27,960
The capital has too many rules.

576
00:32:28,119 --> 00:32:29,319
Many entertainments are forbidden.

577
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,920
For example,
in Tongzhou,

578
00:32:32,319 --> 00:32:34,039
during New Year, we held temple fairs.

579
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:35,359
Tongzhou's wealthy merchants

580
00:32:35,359 --> 00:32:36,480
take turns hiring opera troupes

581
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:37,759
to perform at the fairs.

